# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional: GH token for the sync script to lift API rate limits
# Create at https://github.com/settings/tokens — public-repo read-only is fine.
# Not required for the public Releases endpoint, but useful in CI.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GITHUB_TOKEN=